&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Articulate and follow up collaboration and processes in place around Direction, Production and Development to ensure an optimal delivery and cohesion within the team&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Directly supervise and mentor the Producers who report to you to drive complex topics forward.&amp;nbsp; You are responsible for their performance reviews, career growth, and coaching while looking out for their well-being.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Provide clear, timely and regular communication to ensure that the teams and key stakeholders are engaged and production goals are well understood.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
