&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position&lt;/strong&gt; – Senior Level Designer&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an experienced Senior Level Designer to join the Haven Entertainment Studios project team. The Senior Level Designer will have end-to-end responsibility for PVP and Interiors, crafting exceptional experiences for the player and supporting the overall design vision for the game. You will collaborate closely with several disciplines across the team and leverage your passion for design to inspire those around you, using&amp;nbsp; feedback and data to create fun and challenging&amp;nbsp; content.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Reporting&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Senior Level Designer will report to the Producer.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities and Duties&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design, implement and iterate on&amp;nbsp; PVP Sandbox&amp;nbsp; and interior levels.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with the design team to prioritize features, validate the game’s quality, and ensure&amp;nbsp; the timely delivery of tasks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assess gameplay and flow to ensure desired player experience is achieved.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use feedback and data to maintain and drive the continual development of level content.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Review work and provide constructive feedback.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with the design and development of custom level editing tools and basic scripting.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely across disciplines on all aspects of the development process to ensure design vision is realized.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with the team at large to resolve design challenges.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fix design bugs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
