&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an experienced AI Game Designer to join the Haven Entertainment Studios project team. The Sr AI Game Designer will work closely with the Game director to help shape the creation and development of the game design direction for the next generation of games. They will develop and design AI and emergent game systems that translate the vision into a playable experience. They will work within a collaborative multidisciplinary environment to ensure the delivery of high quality features with the consumer needs always at the forefront.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Reporting Line&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;The Senior AI Game Designer will report to the Production Director.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role and Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with the Game Director to shape the direction and break it down into a clear set of features, deliverables, and tasks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop the vision for AI systems and Game play Ingredient, create emergent experiences between the AI and the player, while coherently integrating the PvE and PvP dimensions of the gameplay experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design, implement, and tune AI systems, behaviours and game play ingredient throughout all stages of production to create exceptional player experiences&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with an interdisciplinary team and act as a regular point of contact within that team, as well as with leadership and other creative and technical co-owners, to ensure cohesion across the work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate game design through multiple means to effectively ensure that gameplay intentions and the work to be done are understood by all team members&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with the Pod Producer to define a clear product vision that supports the identification and prioritization of features to be developed for each production milestone&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Adapt&amp;nbsp; features and systems based on player feedback, while ensuring the coherence of AI systems in relation to the evolution of gameplay mechanics and the addition of new game modes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Required Experience and Skills&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Extensive experience in game design, with at least one shipped title in this field&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong understanding of game design principles, with a focus on AI behaviours and emergent systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong Understanding of core game AI systems — navigation, perception, awareness, state machines, Behavior Trees / State Trees, and AI data tuning in Unreal — to effectively design, adjust, and communicate expected AI behaviors with programmers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong ability to work directly in the Unreal Engine editor to tune parameters, identify issues through configuration analysis, and create rapid prototypes to support the initial validation needs of new features&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understanding and experience in effectively integrating player data and metrics into the design process&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent ability to organize and structure one’s own work and communicate effectively with a diverse audience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Assets&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
